org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.io

Class TcasesOpenApiIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.io.TcasesOpenApiIO

  • public final class TcasesOpenApiIO
extends Object
    Defines methods for generating Tcases documents from OpenAPI definitions.

    OpenAPI definitions must conform to OAS version 3. See https://swagger.io/specification/#specification.
